5.2.0 (2009/4/21)


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ganga/python/Ganga
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Updated tests for Batch backend.


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ganga/python/Ganga/Lib/Batch
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Several updates to the Batch backends. The bugs and features requests
numbered 35994, 36651, 45219, 47814 and 49078 have been addressed. The
most important change is that batch jobs killed by the batch system
itself (like if they overrun their CPU limit) are now correctly
registered in Ganga as failed.


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ganga/python/GangaAtlas
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Athena:
------
* New: Rewrite of Athena.prepare() 
  - New CMT detection and tarfile creation for Panda
  - use panda_prepare(LCG=True) or panda_prepare(NG=True)
    to use this routine with LCG or NG or Batch backends
  Old prepare() has been renamed to prepare_old()
* dependent now on panda-client external 

AthenaMC:
---------
* New: AthenaMCPandaRTHandler.py
  Adding new Run Time Handler for the Panda backend. Simplified 
  AthenaMC interface: production_name is now inactive, and 
  process_name can be used to fill in for run_number as well. 
  Finally, an attempt to extract process_name for input job 
  options and/or dataset has been implemented, reducing the 
  total number of mandatory fields. Native backend member to 
  select a given storage can be used to replace se_name as well. 
  Arguments in extraIncArgs can be put in extraArgs as well, 
  using the dedicated key word . Added length check on output 
  dataset names.

Tasks:
-----
* Removed setting the inputGenerator file from tasks, 
  this is set in AthenaMC automatically
* Added safeguard so that manually resubmitting split jobs 
  that failed on submission works

scripts:
-------
* Use new prepare() method


